<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B-</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树索引是一个典型的数据结构，其包含的组件主要有以下几个：</span></li>
 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>叶子节点：包含的条目直接指向表里的数据行。叶子节点之间彼此相连，一个叶子节点有一个指向下一个叶子节点的指针。分支节点：包含的条目指向索引里其他的分支节点或者叶子节点。</span></li>
 </ul>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:40px'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>根节点：一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> B-</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树索引只有一个根节点，实际上就是位于树的最顶端的分支节点。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>基于这种树形数据结构，表中的每一行都会在索引上有一个对应值。因此，在表中进行数据查询时，可以根据索引值一步一步定位到数据所在的行。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B-</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树索引可以进行全键值、键值范围和键值前缀查询，也可以对查询结果进行</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> ORDER BY </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>排序。但</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> B-</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树索引必须遵循左边前缀原则，要考虑以下几点约束：</span></li>
 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>查询必须从索引的最左边的列开始。</span></li>
 </ul>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:40px'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>查询不能跳过某一索引列，必须按照从左到右的顺序进行匹配。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:40px'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>存储引擎不能使用索引中范围条件右边的列。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;font-size:13.5pt'><span style='font-weight:bold;
font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=zh-CN>B</span><span style='font-weight:bold;
font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=en-US>+Tree </span><span style='font-weight:
bold;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"' lang=zh-CN>索引</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MySql</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引数据结构对经典的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+Tree</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>进行了优化，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+ </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树中各个页之间是通过双向链表连接的，叶子节点中的数据是通过单向链表连接的。在原</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+Tree</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的基础上，增加一个指向相邻叶子节点的链表指针，就形成了带有顺序指针的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+Tree</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，提高区间访问的性能。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>如果不存储数据，那么就会存储更多的键值，相应的树的阶数（节点的子节点树）就会更大，树就会更矮更胖，如此一来我们查找数据进行磁盘的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> IO </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>次数又会再次减少，数据查询的效率也会更快。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:13.5pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in'><img

width=596 height=393></p>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+ </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树非叶子节点上是不存储数据的，仅存储键值，而</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> B </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树节点中不仅存储键值，也会存储数据。之所以这么做是因为在数据库中页的大小是固定的，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>InnoDB </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>中页的默认大小是</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 16KB</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>另外，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+ </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树的阶数是等于键值的数量的，如果我们的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> B+ </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树一个节点可以存储</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 1000 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>个键值，那么</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 3 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>层</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> B+ </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树可以存储</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 1000</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>×</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>1000</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>×</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>1000=10 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>亿个数据。一般根节点是常驻内存的，所以一般我们查找</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 10 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>亿数据，只需要</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> 2 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>次磁盘</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> IO</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>因为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> B+</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>树</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>索引的所有数据均存储在叶子节点，而且数据是按照顺序排列的。那么</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> B+ </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>树使得范围查找，排序查找，分组查找以及去重查找变得异常简单。而</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> B </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>树因为数据分散在各个节点，要实现这一点是很不容易的。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>实际上</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> B</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>-</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>树</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>我们也可以对各个节点加上链表。这些不是它们之前的区别，是因为在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> MySQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> InnoDB </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>存储引擎中，索引就是这样存储的。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in'><span style='font-weight:bold;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:13.5pt' lang=zh-CN>Hash</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-weight:bold;font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt' lang=zh-CN>索引</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>哈希（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Hash</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>）一般翻译为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>“</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>散列</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>”</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，也有直接音译成</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>“</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>哈希</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>”</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的，就是把任意长度的输入（又叫作预映射，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>pre-image</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>）通过散列算法变换成固定长度的输出，该输出就是散列值。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引也称为散列索引或哈希索引。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MySQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>目前仅有</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> MEMORY </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>存储引擎和</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> HEAP </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>存储引擎支持这类索引。其中，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MEMORY </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>存储引擎可以支持</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> B-</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树索引和</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引，且将</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>当成默认索引。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引不是基于树形的数据结构查找数据，而是根据索引列对应的哈希值的方法获取表的记录行。哈希索引的最大特点是访问速度快，但也存在下面的一些缺点：</span></li>
 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MySQL </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>需要读取表中索引列的值来参与散列计算，散列计算是一个比较耗时的操作。也就是说，相对于</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> B-</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树索引来说，建立哈希索引会耗费更多的时间。</span></li>
 </ul>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:40px'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>不能使用</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引排序。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:40px'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引只支持等值比较，如</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>“=”“IN()”</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>或</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>“&lt;=&gt;”</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:40px'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引不支持键的部分匹配，因为在计算</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> HASH </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>值的时候是通过整个索引值来计算的。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>
